{"tid":776688,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"沙中綫工程醜聞不絕","createTime":"2018-08-12T10:03:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-12T10:54:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b70f5c83e6e4a111793fb0d93cb54526e42f2275","tid":776688,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T10:03:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180812/20474676\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180812%2F20474676&d=CaCyDFBDAo9jvYXwudbz%2BWMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=c5c7a875\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180812%2F20474676&h=82b66a15\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180812/20474676</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年08月12日 <br />\n<br />\n沙中綫工程醜聞不絕<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180812/large/a0202a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180812%2Flarge%2Fa0202a.gif&h=9cdab2cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】沙中綫工程自2012年動工以來，因工程延誤超支至近千億元，成為香港有史以來最貴鐵路，通車日期亦延遲一年。目前超支撥款仍有待提交立法會審批，又連續爆出多宗偷工減料醜聞，工程成本會否進一步上升，以及通車日期會否再延遲仍是未知之數。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵去年底宣佈沙中綫整體工程成本798億元，因土瓜灣站考古及會展站工程延誤等因素，超支至971.63億元。政府仍在審核港鐵提交賬目，完成後才提交立法會財委會申請追加撥款。<br />\n<br />\n在舊賬未清之際，沙中綫工程又連續爆出多宗醜聞，問題比之前延誤更嚴重。當中紅磡站是重災區，月台連續牆鋼筋未有接駁螺絲帽，承建商禮頓疑安排工人剪短鋼筋「裝假狗」，有消息指被剪鋼筋達5,000支。<br />\n<br />\n北面連接隧道亦出現滲水，鋼筋亦被指未完全接駁螺絲帽。政府更發現港鐵未經批准修改月台設計圖則，連續牆的螺絲頭數量大幅減少2,000多個。紅磡站月台結構安全成疑，如何善後亦未知，隨時成為沙中綫的無底深潭。<br />\n<br />\n■記者麥志榮  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n沙中綫沉降疑平價國產鑽機肇禍　損地層結構會展站水管壓至變形<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n土瓜灣民居震出裂縫"},{"pid":"806a39f9ea7ab62efcbed26cd783dabb579d456d","tid":776688,"uid":53524,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T10:03:46.000Z","msg":"今日紅日無野爆"},{"pid":"c00cca3646ba536e70e24b76cbd50686b3e1ac82","tid":776688,"uid":66324,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T10:19:15.000Z","msg":"爆完又點, 港鐵同禮頓咪又安然無恙 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ee0ea864c46ac2261627c016f7134f5612b3956","tid":776688,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T10:31:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19423301f899fa9f1a3f7c17757457e38ff37427","tid":776688,"uid":200253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T10:54:48.000Z","msg":"咪又係會繼續撥錢比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}